Terms & Conditions

Free version
        
 Car Expense app provides a free version which you can access limited feature of the app.
                    
 Pro user
               
 Subscribe to access all pro features, to add unlimited fuel and maintenance, create unlimited reminders and support the development of the app.
 Cancel at any time in Settings -> Apple ID at least one day before each renewal date.
 Plan automatically renews until canceled. 
                 
  Privacy Policy 
                    
   Car Expense app don't collect and manage user data.
   Any data you enter in the app is writer directly into your device and it is not accessible to us.
